    "description": "在这个世界中，人类的存在已经成为久远的记忆。玩家将扮演游戏的主人公克利德，一只惹事生非、醉醺醺的蜗牛，刚刚被逐出了家乡的要塞。在忠实而健谈的萤火虫贝露的陪伴下，克利德会遇到一群奇特的被放逐者，并找到一个可以称之为家的地方。在这群新朋友中，克利德发现了新的目标：消灭肆虐这片土地的神秘鼻涕虫瘟疫。<br><br>《蜗牛克利德》是一款独特的俯视角射击游戏，游戏的核心是角色驱动的叙事和专注的战斗。作为克利德，玩家将经历一个关于放逐、友谊和背叛的故事，并体验一只不为同类所接受的爱惹麻烦、不守规矩的蜗牛的冒险经历。探索一个充满威胁和挑战的危险世界，在那里，生存的关键在于战略布局、精准的枪战，还有敌人的行为。发现鼻涕虫瘟疫肆虐世界背后的真相，拯救这片土地，使其免遭最终毁灭。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/56457a083aef7fa124180d6f4bef5ff3.poster.avif?t=1709554613\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/56457a083aef7fa124180d6f4bef5ff3.webm?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/56457a083aef7fa124180d6f4bef5ff3.mp4?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用枪炮、榴弹和独特的蜗牛壳发挥创意，智胜敌人。充分利用环境并学会战略布局以取得胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/29e52e6c2be91e64470ad52d683eef42.poster.avif?t=1709554613\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/29e52e6c2be91e64470ad52d683eef42.webm?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/29e52e6c2be91e64470ad52d683eef42.mp4?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>害羞的刺猬、萨满乌龟、哑巴蝙蝠、忍者蛙和独眼变色龙：这些都是阿拉斯托耳的成员。每次任务结束后回家休息、储备资源、升级设备，并发展友谊。了解这些独特的角色并揭开他们的过去，找出故事的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/17ea02822fda5d0fe487b5e0bacfe323.poster.avif?t=1709554613\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/17ea02822fda5d0fe487b5e0bacfe323.webm?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/17ea02822fda5d0fe487b5e0bacfe323.mp4?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>沼泽、沙漠、山脉、岛屿……每个任务都会展现一个等待被发现的新地点。帮助当地居民抵御鼻涕虫的威胁，成为他们的英雄！而且不要忘记保持敏锐的眼光：探索每个关卡，寻找额外的好东西。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/553724a2667bc9a3858332e758abd5e0.poster.avif?t=1709554613\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/553724a2667bc9a3858332e758abd5e0.webm?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/553724a2667bc9a3858332e758abd5e0.mp4?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在每个任务结束时都有强大的威胁等着你。需要研究敌人的行为，关注细节，并明智地选择武器以在这些危险的遭遇中幸存下来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/03c7cd4100d5f05a356e63c6475db7cf.poster.avif?t=1709554613\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/03c7cd4100d5f05a356e63c6475db7cf.webm?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597580/extras/03c7cd4100d5f05a356e63c6475db7cf.mp4?t=1709554613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>射击并不总是唯一的答案。使用武器和智慧来解决谜题、寻找秘密并在故事中前进。有时，答案就隐藏在显而易见的地方……",
